meanings: 음식에 대해 I don't like how it tastes.
음식에 대해 This food doesn't suit my taste.
(예감·추측 등이) be right, prove right, come true (=들어맞다)
(얻어맞다) be hit, be struck; (뺨을) be slapped; (여러 차례) be beaten
(총·벼락 등을) be hit (by), (총을) be shot, (벼락을) be struck
